Simon Gunnarsson (borås basket) hurt his shoulder about 1 year ago and doctors wanted him to have a surgery. Simon decided not to go through with the surgery after talking with me and @sethronland!
The shoulder is no longer a problem and he played most of last seasons games! 
Focus is now to get in as good shape as possible before next season starts and stay away from more injuries!
